cerpt_area": {"text": "路透社 7 日援引一名伊朗消息人士的话说，伊朗拒绝与美国达成「任何临时性停火」。 这名没有透露姓名的伊朗官员说，伊朗为与美国达成「持久和平」协议设定了「先决条件」，包括敌方立即停止袭击伊朗，承诺不再对伊发动袭击并赔偿伊方损失等。他说，该和平协议应允许伊朗对通过霍尔木兹海峡的船只收取费用。英媒：伊朗消息人士称伊朗拒绝「临时停火」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-480a7d58420d3632a39f41a1ded3b7ae_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2024942392235614830"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI3aP5sPmG9tQdEAMaCTExOTA1NzA3MSDv6NPOBjAAOKkGQAtyEzIwMjQ5NDIzOTIyMzU2MTQ4MzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1775598140.831863", "card_id": "Q_2024080354932261220", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 17}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待大学里将逃课看作「自由」或「反叛」的行为？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "每次看到同学逃课，总有人说这是大学精神的一种体现，是拒绝填鸭式教育的「反叛」。但我总在想，这种所谓的自由，究竟是真的自由，还是为偷懒找借口？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ef1b387dc8de0954b2b72234e453c8c4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2024080354932261220"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI3aP5sPmG9tQdEAMaCTExOTAyODkwNCCao8fOBjAAOBhADHITMjAyNDA4MDM1NDkzMjI2MTIyMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1775598140.832218", "card_id": "Q_660955841", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "手机自带系统杀毒功能，是不是摆设？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "用了这么多年的手机 ，用了那么多牌子，感觉这个杀毒功能一直没杀过实质性的东西，全是安全，真的是手机安全，还是只是个摆设啊？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2215c136bdcad548bea73965edbdedaa_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_co